<html>
                <body style='font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333;'>
                    <div style='max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; border: 1px solid #ddd; border-radius: 10px;'>
                        <h2 style='color: #d9534f; text-align: center;'>Low Stock Alert</h2>
                        <p>Hello,</p>
                        <p>This is an automated alert to inform you that the stock for the following book is running low.</p>
                        
                        <div style='background-color: #f8f9fa; border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 15px; border-radius: 5px; margin: 20px 0;'>
                            <h3 style='margin-top: 0; color: #2c3e50;'>Book Details</h3>
                            <p><strong>Title:</strong> {BookTitle}</p>
                            <p><strong>Author:</strong> {AuthorName}</p>
                            <p><strong>Current Stock:</strong> {StockQuantity}</p>
                        </div>

                        <p>Please take the necessary action to restock this item.</p>
                        
                        <hr style='border: 1px solid #eee; margin: 30px 0;'>
                        <p style='text-align: center; font-size: 0.9em; color: #777;'>&copy; @DateTime.Now.Year Connect2us. All rights reserved.</p>
                    </div>
                </body>
            </html>